{"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/setlanguage:"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration"]]},"sections":[],"metadata":{"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"setLanguage:"}],"role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"+ "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"setLanguage:"}],"title":"setLanguage:","modules":[{"name":"PushwooshCore"}],"symbolKind":"method","roleHeading":"Type Method","externalID":"c:objc(pl)PWConfiguration(cm)setLanguage:"},"kind":"symbol","identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/setLanguage:"},"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"abstract":[{"text":"Sets custom application language for localized notifications.","type":"text"}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"+ (","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:v","text":"void","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"text":"setLanguage:","kind":"identifier"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSString","text":"NSString","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"kind":"text","text":" *) "},{"text":"language","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}],"languages":["occ"],"platforms":["iOS"]}]},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The language code (e.g., “en”, “de”, “fr”, “es”) or nil to reset to device language"}]}],"name":"language"}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"level":2,"text":"Discussion","type":"heading","anchor":"discussion"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Override the device language for Pushwoosh to enable:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Sending notifications in a specific language","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Language-based segmentation","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Supporting in-app language switching","type":"text"}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Must be a lowercase two-letter code according to ISO-639-1 standard."}]},{"level":2,"text":"Example","type":"heading","anchor":"Example"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Support in-app language selection:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["class LanguageManager {","","    static let shared = LanguageManager()","","    var currentLanguage: String {","        didSet {","            applyLanguageChange()","        }","    }","","    func applyLanguageChange() {","        \/\/ Update Pushwoosh language for targeted notifications","        Pushwoosh.configure.setLanguage(currentLanguage)","","        \/\/ Update user tags","        Pushwoosh.configure.setTags([","            \"language\": currentLanguage,","            \"language_changed_date\": Date()","        ])","","        \/\/ Update app UI","        Bundle.setLanguage(currentLanguage)","        NotificationCenter.default.post(name: .languageDidChange, object: nil)","","        Logger.info(\"App language changed to: \\(currentLanguage)\")","    }","","    func resetToDeviceLanguage() {","        Pushwoosh.configure.setLanguage(nil)","        currentLanguage = Locale.current.languageCode ?? \"en\"","    }","}"]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"“zh” (Chinese), “ja” (Japanese), “ko” (Korean), “ru” (Russian)"}]}]}],"references":{"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore":{"role":"collection","url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","kind":"symbol","title":"PushwooshCore","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"